@page "/privacy"

<PageTitle>Privacy Policy — Signavex</PageTitle>

<div class="animate-fade-in max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface tracking-tight mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
        <p><strong class="text-on-surface">Effective Date:</strong> March 1, 2026</p>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-on-surface mb-2">1. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p>When you create an account, we collect your email address and password (stored as a salted hash). If you subscribe to a paid plan, payment information is collected and processed by Stripe — we do not store your credit card details on our servers. We do not collect social media profiles or other personal data.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-on-surface mb-2">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p>Your email is used solely for account authentication and essential service communications. We do not send marketing emails or share your information with advertisers.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-on-surface mb-2">3. Data Storage</h2>
            <p>Account data is stored in a secured database. Scan results, economic data, and AI briefs are stored server-side and associated with the application, not with individual user accounts.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-on-surface mb-2">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
            <p>The Service integrates with the following third-party services:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
                <li><strong class="text-on-surface">Data Providers</strong> (Polygon.io, Alpha Vantage, FRED): retrieve market and economic data. No personal user data is shared with these providers.</li>
                <li><strong class="text-on-surface">Anthropic</strong>: generates AI-powered market analysis. No personal user data is shared.</li>
                <li><strong class="text-on-surface">Stripe</strong>: processes subscription payments. Stripe collects payment information directly on their hosted checkout page. See <a href="https://stripe.com/privacy" class="text-primary hover:underline" target="_blank">Stripe's Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
                <li><strong class="text-on-surface">SendGrid</strong>: delivers transactional emails (account verification, password reset). Your email address is shared with SendGrid for delivery purposes only. See <a href="https://www.twilio.com/legal/privacy" class="text-primary hover:underline" target="_blank">Twilio/SendGrid Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-on-surface mb-2">5. Cookies</h2>
            <p>The Service uses essential cookies for authentication and session management. We do not use tracking cookies or third-party analytics.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-on-surface mb-2">6. Data Retention</h2>
            <p>Account data is retained as long as your account is active. You may request deletion of your account and associated data by contacting the site administrator.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-on-surface mb-2">7. Security</h2>
            <p>We use industry-standard measures to protect your data, including encrypted connections (HTTPS) and hashed passwords. However, no method of electronic storage is 100% secure.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-on-surface mb-2">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Continued use of the Service after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-on-surface mb-2">9. Contact</h2>
            <p>For privacy-related inquiries, please contact the site administrator.</p>
        </section>
    </div>
</div>
